des:
Totilas products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart home device.
After connecting Alexa to your Totilas in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our "Totilas" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Totilas account in our "Totilas" app;
(3). You need to have some Totilas devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Totilas" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Totilas" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Totilas" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Totilas", and you'll be navigated to "Totilas" login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on device name.”
“Alexa, turn off device name.”
